des:
One Line Joker skill when invoked tells a one line joke

Listen to funny one liners from Joker. You can 'Ask one line joker'

- a joke
- tell me a joke
- give me a joke
- humor me
- make me laugh
- tell a joke
- tell me something
- give me something

DISCLAIMER: One Line Joker may not be suitable for all ages.
